name: Trickstars Together
text:
At the beginning of the Duel, add 1 "Trickstar Candina" and 1 "Trickstar Lilybell" to your Deck. Then, add 1 "Trickstar Holly Angel" to your Extra Deck.
The following effect can be used once per turn. Select 1 non-Link "Trickstar" monster you control, and move that monster to another of your Main Monster Zones.
